This paper involves the use of gene expression programming and multi-objective optimization to model dew point. It falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, specifically in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper also involves the use of optimization techniques, which could place it in the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY) and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
